 * Information: The user can enter password "0000" to enter the GUI of calculate . 
 *				The calculate has twenty and eight button and a Text Field 
 *				GUI: 
 *				            TextField
 *					sin  cos   sec  log
 *					csc  tan   cot  ln
 *					%    /     π   del
